# PHOENIX PROTOCOL - UNIFIED GATEWAY CONFIG V4.4 (FINAL CORS FIX)
# 1. FIX (Juristi): Consolidated all headers into a single block to prevent overrides.
# 2. FIX (Haveri): Implemented dynamic Origin matching to correctly support www and non-www.
# 3. STATUS: Production Ready.

